#: addons/Coastal_Mountainsides.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Four empires head face-to-face, surrounded by two large seas. Along with "
"mountains acting like natural walls, which cannot be crossed at all. "
"However, there is one land bridge that connects the large seas, giving the "
"empires a solution, and the only solution to conquer the whole area."
